FINNEUS dropped back to trail early, traveled two wide around the bend, then angled out nearing the stretch and failed to menace. I'LL STAND TALLER bumped with BIG CITY LIGHTS in the beginning, pressed the pace inside rivals to the half-mile pole then chased the top pair into the turn, continued along the rail through the turn and faded in the drive.

VICTORY MATTERS was forced inward and steadied at the start, raced near the back into the turn, spun three wide into the lane, angled out and failed to rally.
